Code that’s easy to review and safe to ship.
	•	Format: Prettier (100 cols, trailing commas).
	•	Lint: ESLint + @typescript-eslint + security.
	•	Types: TS strict: true; JS requires JSDoc.
	•	Tests: Jest; coverage ≥ 85 %.
	•	Errors: custom Error; no console.log.
	•	Security: no eval; validate input (zod).
	•	Deps: locked versions, npm audit gate.
	•	Commits: Conventional Commits; hooks run lint+scan.
